"{\"post\": {\"heroImage\": \"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/kitchen-blog/images/Blog2_LGInstaviewOven.png?rand=ee99\", \"title\": \"Festive Season Cooking Tips: Deep cleaning after the holiday cooking season\"}, \"article\": {\"introParagraphs\": [\"The holiday season gathers loved ones, fills every corner of the home with warmth, and turns the kitchen into the true centre of festive activity. Between roasting turkeys, air-frying party snacks, baking desserts, and preparing multiple meals back-to-back, your oven works harder during the holidays than at any other time of the year.\", \"And while the joy of cooking is unmatched, the aftermath spills, splatters, greasy trays, and lingering aromas often leave homeowners wondering how to restore their oven to its original shine.\", \"Fortunately, today’s innovations in kitchen appliances, particularly <a href=\\\"https://www.lg.com/sa_en/built-in-appliances/ovens/\\\" class=\\\"brand-link\\\">LG’s range of advanced InstaView™ ovens</a> make festive cooking easier, smarter, and far cleaner. Whether you’ve just survived marathon baking sessions or cooked several large meals in a row, the post-holiday deep clean doesn’t need to feel overwhelming.\", \"With features like EasyClean™, Air Fry, Air Sous-Vide, LG ThinQ™, and highly efficient A+ and A++ energy grades, the modern oven is designed to lighten your workload while elevating your culinary skills.\", \"In this guide, we’ll explore practical festive cooking tips and effective deep cleaning advice alongside how a feature-rich oven can completely transform your holiday culinary experience.\"], \"detailedParagraphs\": [\"\"], \"sections\": [{\"heading\": \"Smart Festive Cooking Starts with Smart Appliances\", \"paragraphs\": [\"Holiday cooking requires precision, timing, and the ability to multitask. An oven like the 76L InstaView™ Electric Oven with Air Fry and Air Sous-Vide gives you the flexibility to prepare multiple dishes efficiently, thanks to its large capacity and 4-in-1 pro cooking functions, including convection, air fry, air sous-vide, and pizza modes. Whether you're roasting meats or crisping vegetables, these cook modes help deliver professional-level results without needing separate countertop appliances.\", \"The InstaView™ feature is especially useful during the busy season. With just two quick knocks on the glass, you can see what's happening inside without opening the door. No heat escapes, no cooking time is disrupted, and your roast remains perfectly tender. This might seem like a small convenience, but when you're preparing several dishes simultaneously, it saves both time and energy.\", \"Holiday cooking becomes even smoother with LG ThinQ™—a smart technology that lets you adjust settings, preheat the oven, set timers, or check progress directly from your smartphone. When you’re juggling guests, wrapping gifts, and prepping meals, this feature helps keep everything running smoothly from anywhere in the house.\"]}, {\"heading\": \"Festive Season Cooking Tips for Better Results\", \"paragraphs\": [\"1. Prepare Your Oven Before the Big Cooking Marathon\", \"Before diving into large festive meals, give your oven a quick prep. If your oven features EasyClean™, a fast steam-based maintenance system, take advantage of it. In just 10 minutes, it softens light residues, making it easier to wipe away dirt before you begin cooking. Starting with a clean oven ensures even temperature distribution and reduces smoke from leftover grease.\", \"2. Use Air Fry for Healthier Holiday Snacks\", \"Party snacks are a holiday essential. With built-in Air Fry, you can enjoy favourites like potato wedges, chicken wings, and vegetable crisps with less oil, keeping things festive without compromising on health. Air Fry also reduces lingering grease compared to traditional deep frying.\", \"3. Cook Large Meals Efficiently with Convection Mode\", \"Convection ovens circulate hot air evenly, helping your <a href=\\\"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/kitchen-blog/beating-the-heat-in-the-kitchen.html\\\" class=\\\"brand-link\\\" data-click=\\\"dishes cook faster and more evenly\\\">dishes cook faster and more evenly</a> When preparing multiple trays of cookies or large roasts, convection mode saves time and energy. An oven with an A+ or A++ energy rating keeps your electricity bills reasonable during the high-usage festive season.\", \"4. Try Air Sous-Vide for Restaurant-Quality Results\", \"Holiday cooking often calls for perfectly cooked meats. The Air Sous-Vide function locks in moisture and tenderness without needing bulky external equipment. Although a vacuum machine is required for sous vide bags, the oven itself manages temperature precisely, creating gourmet dishes with ease.\", \"5. Use InstaView™ to Avoid Heat Loss\", \"Repeatedly opening the oven during holiday cooking can lead to temperature fluctuations. With InstaView™, you simply knock twice to check your dish's progress. This saves energy, protects cooking consistency, and prevents the oven from needing extra time to heat back up.\"]}, {\"heading\": \"Deep Cleaning After the Holiday Cooking Season\", \"paragraphs\": [\"Once the celebrations wind down, your oven likely shows signs of heavy use: splattered sauces, baked-on residue, crumbs, and spills. Here’s how to restore it to pristine condition.\", \"1. Use EasyClean™ for a Quick Refresh\", \"LG ovens featuring EasyClean™ use the power of steam to loosen grime. Simply add water to the bottom of the oven, activate EasyClean™, and let the steam treatment soften residue in minutes. There are no harsh chemicals, no fumes, and no extended downtime; just wipe it clean.\", \"This is perfect for homeowners who dread scrubbing or worry about toxins in traditional oven cleaners.\", \"2. For Stubborn Messes, Use a Deeper Clean Cycle\", \"While EasyClean™ excels at everyday maintenance, some LG models also include more intensive cleaning options for deep post-holiday grime. These cycles break down baked-on grease effortlessly, so you can enjoy a fresh oven ready for the new year.\", \"3. Take Advantage of Removable Oven Door Glass\", \"Some models, such as the <a href=\\\"https://www.lg.com/sa_en/built-in-appliances/ovens/wsezm7225s2/\\\" class=\\\"brand-link\\\" data-click=\\\"LG 60cm Built-in Oven (72L)\\\">LG 60cm Built-in Oven (72L)</a> , feature removable door glass, making it easier to clean crumbs or splatters trapped in between layers. Keeping the glass clear also improves visibility and maintains the oven’s sleek appearance.\", \"4. Clean Accessories Like Telescopic Rails and Racks\", \"Many LG ovens come with telescopic rails, which make handling heavy dishes easier during holiday cooking. These removable rails, along with other oven racks, can be cleaned separately to ensure smooth functionality.\", \"5. Don’t Forget the Exterior\", \"If your oven features a Black Stainless Steel or STS finish, wipe it down with a microfiber cloth and gentle cleaner. This helps maintain its stylish, fingerprint-resistant appearance.\"]}, {\"heading\": \"Designed for Style, Performance, and Convenience\", \"paragraphs\": [\"From the seamless touch control panels of the built-in microwave ovens to the sleek finishes of the InstaView™ range, LG’s appliances blend into modern kitchen décor effortlessly. The harmonious design complements contemporary and traditional spaces alike, and the generous capacities, such as 76 liters, ensure you have enough room for even the largest festive meals.\", \"Whether you’re maintaining your built-in oven bundle with InstaView™, experimenting with ProBake Steam™, or using Scan-to-Cook via ThinQ™, every feature is built to enhance convenience and elevate your cooking experience.\"]}, {\"heading\": \"Conclusion\", \"paragraphs\": [\"Holiday cooking doesn’t need to be chaotic, and cleaning up afterward doesn’t need to be a hassle. With advanced technologies and high energy-efficient designs, LG appliances make festive season cooking far more enjoyable and the cleanup almost effortless.\", \"As you transition from festive feasts to the New Year’s routine, a deep-cleaned oven ensures better performance, improved safety, reduced odours, and more efficient cooking. With the right appliances and a little seasonal maintenance, your kitchen will be ready for anything from everyday dinners to next year’s holiday celebrations. For more information, <a href=\\\"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/kitchen-blog/cooking-for-family-gatherings-guide.html\\\" class=\\\"brand-link\\\" data-click=\\\"read here.\\\">read here.</a>\"]}]}, \"sidebar\": {\"featureTitle\": \"Featured Product\", \"products\": [{\"button\": {\"class\": \"btn-action btn-green\", \"text\": \"Request Enterprise Quote\"}, \"href\": \"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/query/\", \"id\": \"\", \"image\": {\"alt\": \"\", \"src\": \"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/kitchen-blog/images/LGE_SJ_Built-In_Banners_1080-x-1080-Feed_en.jpg\"}, \"name\": \"\"}, {\"id\": \"prod-1780551120932\", \"name\": \"76L Electric Oven | InstaView Oven | Air Fry |\", \"href\": \"https://www.lg.com/sa_en/built-in-appliances/ovens/wsed7613b/\", \"image\": {\"src\": \"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/kitchen-blog/images/thum-1100x7308.jpeg\", \"alt\": \"\"}, \"button\": {\"text\": \"BUY NOW\", \"class\": \"btn-action btn-red\"}}, {\"id\": \"prod-1780551163940\", \"name\": \"76L Electric Oven InstaView Air Sous-Vide\", \"href\": \"https://www.lg.com/sa_en/built-in-appliances/ovens/ws7d7610g/buy/\", \"image\": {\"src\": \"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/kitchen-blog/images/thum-1100x7307.jpeg\", \"alt\": \"\"}, \"button\": {\"text\": \"BUY NOW\", \"class\": \"btn-action btn-red\"}}]}, \"moreToRead\": {\"cards\": [{\"heading\": \"Dazzle Your Guests: Pro Tips & Features for Flawless Festive Feasts with Your LG Induction Hob & ThinQ® Hood\", \"href\": \"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/kitchen-blog/dazzle-your-guest-lg-induction-hob-thinq-hood.html\", \"id\": \"\", \"image\": {\"alt\": \"\", \"src\": \"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/kitchen-blog/images/Blog3_LGInductionHobInduction_.png?rand=d11d\"}, \"text\": \"Festive celebrations are about creating memorable moments, where great flavours meet perfect timing and a relaxed host in the kitchen.\"}, {\"id\": \"card-1780551210359\", \"heading\": \"Festive Season Cooking Tips: Precise temperature control for delicate holiday recipes\", \"text\": \"The festive season is all about coming together over comforting, flavour-filled food. From gently simmered gravies and smooth desserts to perfectly cooked mains\", \"href\": \"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/kitchen-blog/smart-festive-season-cooking.html\", \"image\": {\"src\": \"https://lgkitchenplanner.com/sa_en/kitchen-blog/images/Blog4_LGCooktop.jpeg?rand=c4ba\", \"alt\": \"\"}}], \"sectionTitle\": \"More to Read\"}, \"meta\": {\"title\": \"Festive Season Cooking Tips & Oven Deep Cleaning Guide\", \"description\": \"Discover festive season cooking tips, easy oven deep cleaning steps, and how InstaView™ ovens simplify holiday cooking and post-festival cleanup at home.\"}}"